        <item>
        <title>Version 2.0</title>
        <sparkle:version>2.0</sparkle:version>
        <link>https://sparkle-project.org</link>
        <sparkle:fullReleaseNotesLink>releasenotes.html</sparkle:fullReleaseNotesLink>
        <description>
          <![CDATA[
              <style>
                strong {
                  font-weight: 600;
                }
                ul li {
                  margin-bottom: 0.2em;
                }
              </style>
              <h3>Version 2.0</h3>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Redesigned Interface</strong>: Enjoy a refreshed, modern UI that improves navigation and streamlines workflows across the app.</li>
                <li><strong>Cloud Sync Support</strong>: Projects and settings can now be synced securely across multiple devices using your account.</li>
                <li><strong>Customizable Shortcuts</strong>: Create and manage keyboard shortcuts for almost any action.</li>
                <li>Improved launch performance and reduced memory usage during startup.</li>
                <li>Fixed an issue where notifications could appear twice in some cases.</li>
                <li>Addressed several minor visual glitches in dark mode.</li>
              </ul>
          ]]>
        </description>
